    <stitle>530 and DT-466/408 Diesel Engine Service (1994) - MANIFOLDS - EXHAUST MANIFOLD - INSPECTION</stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="inspect" graphiccount="3">
        <title>INSPECTION</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Visually inspect exhaust manifold for cracks. Replace as required.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Inspect for warpage as follows:
                <emph type="bold">Figure
                    <hotlnk xrefid="ef1050306">3.6</hotlnk>
                </emph>
                :
            </para>
            <step2>
                <para count="1">Install exhaust manifold to cylinder head
                    <emph type="bold">WITHOUT GASKET</emph>. Tighten bolts to specified torque value.
                </para>
            </step2>
            <step2>
                <para count="1">Using a .010 in. (0.25 mm) feeler gauge, measure gap between bolts at manifold flange to
                    cylinder head mating surface.
                </para>
            </step2>
            <step2>
                <para count="1">feeler gauge will pass through, exhaust manifold requires resurfacing.</para>
                <specpara>
                    <important>
                        <para>A MAXIMUM OF 0.025 IN. (0.64 mm) MATERIAL CAN BE GROUND OFF TO CORRECT WARPAGE.</para>
                    </important>
                </specpara>
            </step2>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">If warpage cannot be corrected by grinding, replace exhaust manifold.</para>
            <figure id="ef1050304" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="eg1746" filename="../figeg1/EG1746.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 3.4.</caption>
                <calloutgroup>
                    <callout1>1. Exhaust Manifold</callout1>
                    <callout1>2. Exhaust Manifold Mounting Bolts (12)</callout1>
                </calloutgroup>
            </figure>
            <figure id="ef1050305" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="eg3569" filename="../figeg3/EG3569.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 3.5.</caption>
                <calloutgroup>
                    <callout1>1. Exhaust Manifold</callout1>
                    <callout1>2. Exhaust Manifold Gasket</callout1>
                </calloutgroup>
            </figure>
            <figure id="ef1050306" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="eg1747" filename="../figeg1/EG1747.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 3.6.</caption>
                <calloutgroup>
                    <callout1>1. Feeler Gauge</callout1>
                    <callout1>2. Exhaust Manifold</callout1>
                </calloutgroup>
            </figure>
        </step1>
